[font=Tahoma][size=4][b]Description

“Snu-Snu” is a term for sexual intercourse originally used by a tribe of giant female aliens in the animated television series [i][url=http://knowyourmeme.com/memes/subcultures/futurama]Futurama[/url][/i]. [color=#ffffff][url=http://knowyourmeme.com/memes/cultures/the-internet]Online[/url][/color], the phrase “death by snu snu” is typically used as a humorous reference
in discussions about exceptionally tall or muscular women


Now you can roleplay as one of those giants as well!

To install simply go to Skyrim>Data>Calientetools>Bodyslide>Sliderpresets and paste it on that folder


Feel free to bash/ask questions/mock the author! (keep in mind i will block you if you disrespect the other members)

(If u want the exact same results install the mods given below)
